---
title: Chorizo and Poblano Tortilla Stacks with Lime Crema and DIY Salsa
description: Tortilla stacks are like quesadillas, but leveled up. Quite literally! Savoury enchilada-spiced chorizo, poblanos and gooey cheddar cheese are a match made in heaven. All this big, bold flavour is complemented by a DIY salsa and cooling cilantro-lime crema.
